{{version028}}

A number of effects in the game will call for a random '''greater demon''', among them the monster spell [[Summon Greater Demon]]. This specifically picks a monster from one of two lists, with the given weights<ref>{{source ref|0.28.0|mon-place.cc|3002}}</ref>:
*60% chance of a random [[Demon#Tier-2 Demons|tier-2 demon]]:
**{{monsterlink|Balrug}}
**{{monsterlink|Blizzard demon}}
**{{monsterlink|Cacodemon}}
**{{monsterlink|Green death}}
**{{monsterlink|Hell beast}}
**{{monsterlink|Hellion}}
**{{monsterlink|Lorocyproca}}
**{{monsterlink|Reaper}}
**{{monsterlink|Shadow demon}}
**{{monsterlink|Tormentor}}

*40% chance of a random [[Demon#Tier-1 Demons|tier-1 demon]]:
**{{monsterlink|Brimstone fiend}}
**{{monsterlink|Executioner}}
**{{monsterlink|Hell sentinel}}
**{{monsterlink|Ice fiend}}
**{{monsterlink|Tzitzimitl}}

